beer.beer_description:
Legend has it that the brave men who sailed the Kimberley seas in search of the elusive pearl loved a good beer.

Our master brewer has created a frothy monument to our rich heritage with this delicious, full malt pale ale just bursting with local flavour and deep character. Perfect for slaking a thirst on a hot summers day or stowing a few away on a wild stormy night. Any way you take it, this beer's an absolute pearler!
